title: Olivier Kingue
text:
Juan Olivier Simo Kingue, known as Olivier Kingue (born 20 February 1996) is a <a href="Cameroon">Cameroon</a>ian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="1.%20FK%20P%C5%99%C3%ADbram">1. FK Příbram</a>.
Club career.
He made his professional debut in the <a href="Segunda%20Liga">Segunda Liga</a> for <a href="S.C.%20Olhanense">Olhanense</a> on 28 January 2017 in a game against <a href="S.C.%20Covilh%C3%A3">Sporting Covilhã</a>.
